
[1]delightfully

   DELIGHTFULLY, adv.

   1. In a manner to receive great pleasure; very agreeable; as, we were
   delightfully employed, or entertained.

   2. In a delightful manner; charmingly; in a manner to afford great
   pleasure; as, the lady sings and plays delightfully.
